Group memberships in LDAP are commonly associated with the CN of a user object.  However, if the membership attribute is using anything other than CN, Confluence can't link up the user to the group.

*Relevant values from user object*
{code}
cn: bob
exampleattribute: 1234567890
{code}

*Relevant values from group object*
{code}
uniqueMember: exampleattribute=1234567890,ou=employee,o=company
{code}

In the above setup, user memberships will not be found.

